      "Irregular heartbeats: Patients may experience episodes of skipped beats or irregular rhythms that can cause discomfort.",
      "Fatigue: A general feeling of tiredness that is not relieved by rest can commonly occur.",
      "Dizziness or lightheadedness: Patients may experience episodes of dizziness, especially when standing up or exerting themselves."
